### 7. Lấy danh sách tất cả Purchase Orders
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/purchase-orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Lấy chi tiết Purchase Order theo ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/purchase-orders/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Nhập kho (Import) Purchase Order với Serial
POST http://localhost:8080/api/inventory/purchase-orders/1/import
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "items": [
    {
      "poItemId": 1,
      "serials": [
        "IP14BLK001",
        "IP14BLK002",
        "IP14BLK003",
        "IP14BLK004",
        "IP14BLK005"
      ]
    },
    {
      "poItemId": 2,
      "serials": [
        "SSS23WHT001",
        "SSS23WHT002",
        "SSS23WHT003"
      ]
    }
  ]
}

